title: Gold support main looking for serious duo partner
body:
must be able to play a game or 2 a day, must be no flame, must be able to read a map and have map awareness. 

add me ingame. only want serious duo to climb with...

replies.body: im a serious player and really want to climb currently silver 5 ( almost silver 4) and im down to duo and put time into the game to climb. hit me up.
Ranks mean very little, apart from when you reach high end elo (Diamond 2 upwards)
